      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GEORGE ALEXIS (7) has good early dash but last time was shuffled out the back and missed the frame, finishing fifth (23.94) in a Restricted WIN at this track. Was fast away and placed (23.94) at this track the start prior. Has ability and looks hard to stop. CODY'S STAR (4) has an impeccable record this course, winning all five starts. Below best last time at Q Parklands (30.67) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 11 length seventh. Suited here and expected to run well. WHERE'S MY BEER (1) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing sixth (31.10) at this track in a Grade 5/6. Well placed here and can atone this time. SORRENTO BEACH (2) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
